Name: Hunter of Antiques
About the game: Just one wrong step and you die Hunter of antiques is a hardcore platformer adventure If you loving run, jump, traps and corridors this game is for you. explore dungeon corridors, overcome the traps . Hidden corridors in the dungeon hide secrets and traps. It is up to you to examine the entire prison and find secrets in these forgotten corridors that hide traps, just one wrong step and you die. Be careful at every step. Explore the dungeon Explore all levels, every corner Watch out for traps Spikes Holes Trick floors Lava Labyrinths
